</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-jHkVzv iFnjrD pf-26_ pf-text-1">The Health and Safety Executive (HSE) reports that in health and social care settings, the risk of sudden cardiac arrest is heightened due to the presence of vulnerable individuals with various health conditions.































































